OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer is meeting with
OL,8,Fleaders from the energy, shipping, and
OL,9,Ffinance sectors in Downing Street on
OL,10,FMonday to look at the potential
OL,11,Feconomic damage caused by the ongoing
OL,12,Fconflict in the Middle East.
OL,14,FThe Downing Street discussions are
OL,15,Fexpected to focus on Iran's ongoing
OL,16,Fblockade of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,17,Fwhich has disrupted the vital shipping
OL,18,Froute for the oil and gas industry, as
OL,19,Fwell as supplies of other products
OL,20,Fsuch as fertiliser.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FThe meeting will involve
OL,8,Frepresentatives from energy firms
OL,9,FShell and BP, shipping giant Maersk,
OL,10,Fmaritime insurance specialist Lloyd's
OL,11,Fof London, and banks HSBC and Goldman
OL,12,FSachs.
OL,14,FThe meeting will also hear an update
OL,15,Fon the situation in the region from
OL,16,FMajor General Richard Cantrill, the
OL,17,FUK's maritime operations commander.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FStarmer told reporters Monday's round
OL,8,Ftable would discuss the impact of the
OL,9,Fwar in Iran on Britain's key energy
OL,10,Fand business sectors
OL,12,FThe government has been keen to play
OL,13,Fdown the possibility of fuel
OL,14,Fshortages, with Education Secretary
OL,15,FBridget Phillipson telling
OL,16,Fbroadcasters on Sunday that drivers
OL,17,Fshould fill up their cars as normal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FThis insistence from cabinet ministers
OL,8,Fcomes against a backdrop of
OL,9,Funcertainty, with international
OL,10,Fpartners more dependent on oil from
OL,11,Fthe Middle East implementing fuel
OL,12,Frationing, and UK supermarket Asda
OL,13,Flast week warning of a higher than
OL,14,Fnormal demand for fuel.
OL,16,FThe PM confirmed a second Cobra
OL,17,Fmeeting would be held on Tuesday to
OL,18,Fdiscuss these issues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves is also
OL,8,Fexpected to join a virtual meeting of
OL,9,FG7 finance and energy ministers and
OL,10,Fcentral bank governors, along with
OL,11,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband on Monday.
OL,13,FShe is expected to use her call with
OL,14,FG7 counterparts to urge them to
OL,15,Fembrace green energy, decreasing the
OL,16,Fworld's dependence on volatile fossil
OL,17,Ffuels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
