CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FThis comes as the cost of Brent crude
OL,8,Flifted more than 3% to $117 (#88.42) a
OL,9,Fbarrel at one stage, amid continued
OL,10,Fattacks by the US and Israel on Iran,
OL,11,Fand with the Iranian-backed Houthi
OL,12,Frebels also entering the war over the
OL,13,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
