PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FThe price of oil had briefly fallen
OL,8,Fafter US President Donald Trump
OL,9,Fappeared to show signs of de-
OL,10,Fescalation, writing on Truth Social
OL,11,Fthat he was postponing his previous
OL,12,Fthreats to obliterate Iran's power
OL,13,Finfrastructure - something he would
OL,14,Flater confirm was postponed even
OL,15,Ffurther.
OL,17,FThis climbdown was coupled with the
OL,18,Fassertion that negotiations with Iran
OL,19,Fwere heading in the right direction,
OL,20,Fnegotiations Starmer later confirmed,
OL,21,Fthough Iran continued to deny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FDespite this, the PM and cabinet
OL,8,Fministers have continued to insist
OL,9,Fthey are planning for every
OL,10,Feventuality, stating it would be wrong
OL,11,Fto assume a swift end to the conflict.
OL,13,FThis uncertainty is only compounded by
OL,14,Fthe US's deployment of a further 3,500
OL,15,Ftroops to the region, and the
OL,16,Fpresident's offhand remarks that he is
OL,17,Fconsidering seizing both Iran's oil
OL,18,Fand its major fuel hub, Kharg Island.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
