CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FLast week, the chairman of Asda
OL,8,Frejected accusations that petrol
OL,9,Fsellers might be "profiteering" from
OL,10,Fhigher pricing in recent weeks, as
OL,11,Fsome of the supermarket's forecourts
OL,12,Freported "temporary" fuel shortages.
OL,14,FWith petrol above 150p per litre for
OL,15,Fthe first time in two years, Allan
OL,16,FLeighton, executive chairman of Asda
OL,17,Fsaid the retailer had seen bumper
OL,18,Fdemand from drivers in response to the
OL,19,Fvolatility in prices due to the war in
OL,20,Fthe Middle East, leading to "tight"
OL,21,Fsupply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FHe said: "Our fuel volumes are up
OL,8,Fquite significantly and clearly demand
OL,9,Fhas been outstripping supply.
OL,11,FAlthough he stressed the issue has
OL,12,Fonly affected "the odd pump" at a
OL,13,Fsmall number of its petrol forecourts,
OL,14,Fhighlighting no forecourts have been
OL,15,Ffully short of fuel.
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
