OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774966279
OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FAsked on Monday whether the government
OL,8,Fwas planning for shortages of this
OL,9,Ftype, the prime minister's spokesman
OL,10,Freplied: "We'll always plan for all
OL,11,Feventualities," insisting: "As the PM
OL,12,Fhas said, and as the government has
OL,13,Fsaid, and indeed industry has said,
OL,14,Ffuel production and imports are
OL,15,Fcontinuing.
OL,17,F"The UK benefits from a diverse and
OL,18,Fresilient supply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
