OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,F"Petrol stations in the UK are well-
OL,8,Fstocked nationally, and any suggestion
OL,9,Fotherwise is incorrect."
OL,11,F"We'd be left so weak, and so exposed
OL,12,Fif any of those individuals were in
OL,13,Fgovernment," Starmer said of his
OL,14,Fpolitial rivals at the launch of his
OL,15,Fparty's local election campaign
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
