OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FOpposing this, the Conservative leader
OL,8,FKemi Badenoch called for a cut in VAT
OL,9,Fon domestic energy bills and the
OL,10,Fscrapping of green taxes on power
OL,11,Fgeneration, saying these measures will
OL,12,Fcut bills by #200.
OL,14,FThe proposal has been criticised by
OL,15,Fsome for its universal approach,
OL,16,Fsomething former prime minister Liz
OL,17,FTruss was criticised for in the
OL,18,Funiversal support package her
OL,19,Fgovernment offered consumers to cope
OL,20,Fwith rising bills at the start of the
OL,21,FUkraine-Russia conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
