OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FLabour have already announced a
OL,8,Fsupport package for those who rely on
OL,9,Fheating oil to heat their homes, a
OL,10,Fprocess not covered by the energy
OL,11,Fprice cap and liable to sharp
OL,12,Fincreases with the volatile market.
OL,14,FLast year, around 90% of crude oil
OL,15,Frefined in the UK ` which is used to
OL,16,Fproduce petrol ` was imported, with
OL,17,Faround 1% of this imported from the
OL,18,FMiddle East, most coming from the US
OL,19,Fand Norway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
