OL,3,CStarmer to meet with energy bosses as
OL,4,CIran war causes further spike in oil
OL,5,Cprice
OL,7,FAround 7% of diesel is imported from
OL,8,Fthe Middle East.
OL,10,FUK refinery production of petrol, from
OL,11,Fcrude oil, exceeded demand in 2025,
OL,12,Faccording to official data.
